node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JEREMY STELLA in Valensole. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
Hello pack! 
The famous lavender fields of the south of France! 🌸
We're over 700k here, it's really amazing, thanks to all who enjoy my world.  Here I share outdoor adventures, a human/animal relationship, my love for nature and beautiful landscapes. I'm happy to be able to touch people in a positive way and share beautiful values with you.
Big thanks to @revolutionrace for sending me this beautiful clothes! 
I've been using their clothes daily for almost 2 years now and they are amazing. Thanks guys! Proud to be part of @revolutionrace team 🔥!

I wish you all a great Sunday! Stay wild ❤️🐺

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JEREMY STELLA in France. May be an image of 1 person, beard and outdoors.

node.text:
Hello pack! 
Father and son! Today is Father's Day and I am very proud to tell you that I consider Njörd as my son. Summer is coming and every year at this time many animals are abandoned, this is a reality and we must denounce it! Animals are often abandoned by the people on whom they depend and who are supposed to care for them. I would like to insist on the word "depend" because it is important.  Our pets are dependent on us like childrens. That is why it is important to remember that beyond the abandonment, there is a real traumatic experience for the animal, both physically and psychologically. 

Living with animals is a huge commitment for many years and it can become a strain for some people when they go on holiday. Think about it first! When I got Njörd I knew it would become a huge part of my life. I spend many hours outside with him every day, it is a reality. I don't play video games for hours, I don't go out every night with friends to party, and if I go somewhere, I take him with me whenever possible! I have to think of him and his needs first. He is big part of my lifestyle, he is my son!
Thank you for reading me and have a nice sunday everyone ❤️🐺
⁣_________________________________
⁣👉 All my outdoor gear: @revolutionrace. /AD
